<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但都完全沒有人出來，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我只好死心回家了──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個……<delay20 />雖然我已經跟你約好<delay8 />
要去你家玩了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Apologize" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是真的很抱歉！<delay20 />我那天<delay8 />
